tag_list: web-development, php, joomla, drupal, wordpress, moodle, intranet, pms, dompin, collabcube, digital-marketing, ecommerce, portals, seo, sem, ppc, kms, web-applications
overview:
Metanest is an internet research and development company that focuses on building websites and web-applications and marketing them to provide fully integrated services to its clients.

Our domain expertise includes development of content managed system (Joomla, Drupal, wordpress) based websites, E-commerce and B2B portals, social media portals, workflow management systems, custom web applications and E-learning solutions.

We offer multi-channel marketing services to our clients, to help market their product, service or brand digitally.

Our service includes search engine optimization, social network campaigns, viral marketing, pay-per-click advertising, SMS marketing and lots more.

Product portfolio:

Dompin: a suite of web-applications which allows companies to instantly setup their intranet and extranet or manage their projects and human resources easily

Collabcube: an advanced collaboration tool for managing internal communications along with strong PMS workflow enabling organizations define and manage processes in an efficient manner
